类 SensorsScenarioModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openintents.tools.simulator.model.SensorsScenarioModel

  • public class SensorsScenarioModel
extends java.lang.Object
    SensorsScenarioModel keeps scenario data: the list of all states in the scenario and information about playing them, like start/current/end position.
